<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>About - Oluwaseye Oyadiran</title>
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@300;400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <style>
        :root {
            --border-radius: 10px;
            --font-size-xl: 2.5rem;
            --font-size-lg: 1.8rem;
            --font-size-md: 1.1rem;
            --font-size-sm: 0.9rem;
            --black: #1c1c1c;
            --gray-light: #f0f0f0;
        }

        body {
            font-family: "Poppins", sans-serif;
            background-color: #2C2C54;
            color: white;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .about-hero {
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            max-width: 1000px;
            margin: 50px auto;
            background-color: #1c1c1c;
            border-radius: var(--border-radius);
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);
            align-items: flex-start; /* Align top */
        }

        /* Profile (Left) */
        .about-hero .profile {
            flex: 0 0 220px;
            min-width: 220px;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: flex-start;
            padding: 30px 20px;
        }

        .profile img {
            width: 180px;
            height: auto;
            border-radius: var(--border-radius);
            object-fit: cover;
            transition: transform 0.3s ease;
            margin-top: 20px; /* ðŸ‘ˆ moves image down slightly */
        }

        .profile img:hover {
            transform: scale(1.05);
        }

        /* Content (Right) */
        .about-hero .content {
            flex: 2;
            padding: 40px 30px;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
        }

        .content h1 {
            font-size: var(--font-size-xl);
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            color: white;
        }

        .content h2 {
            font-size: var(--font-size-lg);
            margin: 25px 0 15px;
            color: white;
        }

        .content p {
            font-size: var(--font-size-md);
            line-height: 1.7;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
        }

        /* Life categories */
        .life-categories {
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            gap: 15px;
            margin-top: 10px;
        }

        .category-card {
            background-color: #2C2C54;
            color: white;
            padding: 20px;
            flex: 1 1 calc(50% - 15px);
            border-radius: var(--border-radius);
            text-align: center;
            transition: transform 0.3s ease, background-color 0.3s ease;
            cursor: pointer;
            min-width: 120px;
        }

        .category-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
            background-color: #3d3d6b;
        }

        .category-card h3 {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: var(--font-size-md);
        }

        .back-link {
            display: inline-block;
            margin-top: 30px;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            background-color: #2C2C54;
            color: white;
            border-radius: var(--border-radius);
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 500;
            transition: background 0.2s, color 0.2s;
            align-self: start;
        }

        .back-link:hover {
            background-color: white;
            color: #2C2C54;
        }

        /* Responsive */
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .about-hero {
                flex-direction: column;
            }
            .category-card {
                flex: 1 1 100%;
            }
            .profile {
                padding: 20px;
                justify-content: center;
            }
            .profile img {
                max-height: 150px;
                margin-top: 10px; /* smaller offset on mobile */
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <div class="about-hero container">

        <div class="profile">
            <img src="../img/Seye.PNG"alt="Oluwaseye Oyadiran">
        </div>

        <div class="content">
            <h1>Hi, I'm Oluwaseye Oyadiran</h1>
            <p>
                I am a Nigerian-born tech professional and aspiring serial entrepreneur, currently building my career in the United States. My foundation was solidified with a Bachelor's in Computer Science, where I complemented my academic studies with hands-on experience through internships at various companies. This unique blend of rigorous technical education and practical industry exposure has equipped me with a comprehensive skill set. Now, I am focused on channeling this expertise, along with a growing business acumen, to identify market opportunities and build innovative solutions. My ultimate goal is to transition from a tech professional into a successful serial entrepreneur, creating ventures that make a meaningful impact.
            </p>

            <h2>Life Categories</h2>
            <div class="life-categories">
                <div class="category-card"><h3>Entry Life</h3></div>
                <div class="category-card"><h3>Professional Life</h3></div>
                <div class="category-card"><h3>Personal Life</h3></div>
                <div class="category-card"><h3>Philanthropy</h3></div>
            </div>

            <a href="/" class="back-link">&larr; Back to Home</a>
        </div>

    </div>

</body>
</html>
